Get Taxon Key for Plants

name_backbone("Plantae")
## # A tibble: 1  11
##   usageKey scient canon rank  status confi match kingdom kingd synonym
## *    <int> <chr>    <chr>   <chr> <chr>    <int> <chr>   <chr>     <int> <lgl>  
## 1        6 Plantae  Plantae KING ACCEP      94 EXACT   Plantae       6 FALSE  
## #  with 1 more variable: verbatim_name <chr>, and abbreviated variable names
## #   scientificName, canonicalName, confidence, matchType, kingdomKey
occ_download(
pred("taxonKey", 6), 
pred("hasGeospatialIssue", FALSE),
pred("hasCoordinate", TRUE),
pred_in("country",c("EC","CO","VE")), 
pred_not(pred_in("basisOfRecord",c("FOSSIL_SPECIMEN","LIVING_SPECIMEN"))),
format = "SIMPLE_CSV"
)
